@startuml SmartCMA_Sequence
title SmartCMA Module - Report Generation Flow

actor Seller
participant Frontend
participant Backend
participant ValuationEngine
participant ReservaAPI
participant PDFService
participant StorageService
participant Database
participant NotificationService

Seller -> Frontend: View completed order dashboard
Frontend -> Frontend: Display SmartCMA CTA
Seller -> Frontend: Click "Ver o meu relatório SmartCMA"

Frontend -> Backend: tRPC smartcma.generate(propertyId)
Backend -> Database: Check if report already generated
Database --> Backend: Return existing report or null

alt Report Already Generated
  Backend --> Frontend: Return cached report
else Generate New Report
  
  Backend -> ValuationEngine: Call PropCheck AVM API
  ValuationEngine -> ValuationEngine: Analyze property attributes
  ValuationEngine -> ValuationEngine: Query transaction database
  ValuationEngine -> ValuationEngine: Calculate price band & confidence
  
  ValuationEngine --> Backend: Return PriceBand {low, mid, high}
  
  Backend -> ValuationEngine: GET /comparables?property_id&limit=5
  ValuationEngine -> ValuationEngine: Match typology + parish + 12 months
  ValuationEngine --> Backend: Return List<Comparable> (anonymised)
  
  Backend -> ReservaAPI: GET /matching-buyers?property_id
  ReservaAPI -> ReservaAPI: Query buyer pool for profile match
  ReservaAPI --> Backend: Return buyer_count (rounded to 5)
  
  Backend -> Backend: Calculate RealityGap (municipality average)
  Backend -> Backend: Calculate DaysOnMarket predictions (3 price points)
  Backend -> Backend: Calculate EnergyImpact (class adjustment)
  
  Backend -> Database: Create SmartCMAReport record
  Database --> Backend: Report saved with id
  
  Backend -> PDFService: Generate PDF from report data
  PDFService -> PDFService: Render React PDF template
  PDFService -> PDFService: Compile to PDF binary
  
  PDFService -> StorageService: Upload PDF to Supabase Storage
  StorageService --> PDFService: Return signed URL (24-hour expiry)
  
  PDFService --> Backend: Return pdf_url
  Backend -> Database: Update SmartCMAReport.pdf_url
  
  Backend -> NotificationService: Send SMARTCMA_READY notification
  NotificationService --> Seller: Email: "Your SmartCMA report is ready"
  
  Backend --> Frontend: Return SmartCMAReport with pdf_url
end

Frontend -> Seller: Display report page
Seller -> Frontend: View price band, comparables, market insights
Seller -> Frontend: Click "Download PDF"
Frontend -> StorageService: Fetch signed URL file
StorageService --> Seller: Download PDF

note right of ValuationEngine
  PropCheck integration
  No direct calls to external AVM
  Cached results where possible
end note

note right of PDFService
  60-second timeout
  Fallback: email PDF later if timeout
end note

@enduml
